milestones.description: Mark Waugh's 173 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for AUS), surpassing Gilchrist's 154
Mark Waugh has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (82) in an innings in ODIs for AUS, going past Gilchrist's 80
This is the highest match aggregate (637) involving teams Australia & West Indies in ODIs
